DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(1,5,2);
$b = random(2,6,2);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Factor the polynomial \((x-$a)(x+$b)^2-(x-$a)^2(x+$b)\). 
Your answer can be written as
\(A(x+B)(x+C)\) with integers \( A\), \(B\), \(C \) and \(B<C\)
$BR where \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $a+$b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  -$a;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(C\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
